{
  "texts": [
    "• Facial anonymization in emotion detection: Facial expression is commonly used in emotion detection among current studies.",
    "However, this detection method may cause a privacy leak in the future if implementing such an emotion detection algorithm to the cabin.",
    "Therefore, it will be important to balance facial anonymization and important information when developing the algorithm.",
    "Using a model, such as GAN network, to create a virtual face might be a solution.",
    "• Occupants' emotion detection: The studies on occupants' emotion detection is in progress."
  ]
}